rComments: ONE OF THE BEST PROFS EVER AT U OF T!!! Allows for class discussions and is very approachable. She knows her stuff and provides tools to apply knowledge to everyday life.

Loved this class! Professor Karam-Zanders is new to UofT. Very approachable. Facilitates interactive lectures by encouraging everyone to participate. Lots of readings and she tests on every one so you need to know them. She has a bit of an unstructured style, which for some may take some getting used to, but I really enjoyed her class.
